opam-version: "2.0"
name: "h2-mirage"
version: "0.2.0"
synopsis: "Mirage support for h2"
description: """
h2 is an implementation of the HTTP/2 specification entirely in OCaml.
h2-mirage provides an Lwt runtime implementation for h2 that targets MirageOS
unikernels."""
